title: Proceedings of the Florida State Horticultural Society
aka: Annual Meeting of the Florida State Horticultural Society
Proceedings of the Annual Meeting of the Florida State Horticultural Society
additional-note: A 1990 renewal record for the book 'Wild Plants for Survival in South Florida' by Julia Frances McHugh Morton mentions that portions were first published in the March 1962 Proceedings of the Florida State Horticultural Society.  The book renewal might cover the articles by Morton in that issue.
